LOCUS       psgRNA_(GB0645)         3172 bp    DNA     circular SYN 15-DEC-2025
DEFINITION  Provides a Short guide RNA which is the combination of the bacterial
            crRNA and tracrRNA into a single guide transcript; it does not
            contain any target site.
